tags.name: Al Etimad Slaughterhouse
tags.note:
Al Etimad is one of the best known and respected slaughterhouses in the Kurdistan Region and Iraq. The facility is well known for its high standards and the cleanliness of its production lines.
Al Etimad was established in 1988.
